org.epics.pvmanager.pva

Class PVATypeAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.epics.pvmanager.pva.PVATypeAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataSourceTypeAdapter<PVAChannelHandler,org.epics.pvdata.pv.PVStructure>

    public abstract class PVATypeAdapter
extends Object
implements DataSourceTypeAdapter<PVAChannelHandler,org.epics.pvdata.pv.PVStructure>
    Type adapter for PVA data source. Will match a channel based on the value type provided and the array flag. Will match the cache based on the type class.
    Author:
    msekoranja
